# Favicon

- The site favicon is stored locally at: [`infinity-store-front/public/favicon.png`](mdc:infinity-store-front/public/favicon.png)
- Root layout references it via Next.js Metadata icons:

```tsx
// src/app/layout.tsx
export const metadata = {
  // ...
  icons: { icon: "/favicon.png" },
};
```

- If new sizes are needed, add variants to `public/` (e.g., `favicon-32x32.png`, `apple-touch-icon.png`) and extend `metadata.icons` accordingly.
